Privacy Policy
This page uses to inform visitors regarding policies with usage of Personal Information if anyone decided to use my app.
Smile Adventures
game is a free application for mobile Android devices. We don't collect any data about you
    in our services and don't interested with it at all. But of course as most free apps we integrate AD services in this game.
    To provide you with better promotions this AD services provided with your Android Advertising ID. To more information you
    can read in AD services web sites.
List of used AD services:
1) Provided by Google
AdMob
2) Cross applications AD service
Tappx
Local storage usage
To save your game progress we use your device local storage. This information not commited to any web services.
So you lose it in case if you remove application from your device.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about my Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact me.
